Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:47.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:49.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a powerful miasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful!\NThe evil is coming closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is it?!\NJust hurry and show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:12.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?!\NThe ground is melting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:25.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this! Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:35.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:42.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:44.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:46.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:54.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:10.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?! I was just about to have\na good fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was just big,\nand not much else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:17.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a letdown. His appearance\nwas so deceptive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But all's well and nothing could\nbe better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:31.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, traveling monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:46.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Our village has been tormented\nby that demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:47.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By {\i1}that{\i0} demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:53.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We shall have a feast for you\nto show our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:03:58.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This was just part of\nmy training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:03.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see. But it's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:09.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The pretty girls of the village\neagerly await you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:10.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if that is the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, since you're being\nso kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Buddha will punish me\nif I don't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:21.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Changing his mind because\nof the young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He really {\i1}is{\i0} a lecher priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:45.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These beans are so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so yummy! They're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been so long since\nwe've had such great food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:54.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sango?\NYou haven't touched your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:58.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... I can see in your palm\nthat you will be blessed with children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:02.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miss, will you be army children?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:04.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll have as many as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fifteen, sixteen...\NIt makes no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:12.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:14.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Hey... Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't just sit there and watch!\NHelp me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you father\ntwo, even three children?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:26.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old woman, you're always\nso healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I still can bear a child\nor two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:43.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even in this age, they had\nlively family communions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's nice to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's a family communion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:48.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:52.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, moms, dads and grandparents\nand siblings all dining together and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,enjoying each other's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:55.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's nice about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such bad manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:12.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you lie down right after eating,\nyou'll end up a cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:31.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was a bit concerned\nabout you, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I came... only to find you\nbattling a giant centipede.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When the fighting's on,\nyou're nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:41.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you always appear\nat times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:42.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a schemer you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:44.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, come now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:47.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where've you been, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even an old one like me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,has some secrets\nhe'd prefer to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:01.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You give me the creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:23.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so full.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:38.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quietly, silently...\ntippy-tippy-toe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:55.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There it comes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've heard of child spirits\nlingering on{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:05.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}in an old mansion like this,\nbut is that all this is?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:22.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:23.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gotta pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:24.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is not the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:41.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My goodness...\NWhat a way to be awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:13.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want to pee again?\NYou can go by yourself, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:33.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's come sneaking into my bed!\NSuch luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:36.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come and join me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're still\nangry about earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:56.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The old woman was just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's all that ruckus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:08.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!\NYou don't have to be so angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's sleepwalking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:30.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes! Can't you be more quiet\nwhen you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:31.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango is possessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:48.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:50.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:00.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:02.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:08.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She slapped him before\nshe came to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that someone\nbewitched Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:14.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But who would bewitch her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:21.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't sense anything suspicious\naround here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:23.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga! When did you\nhop onto Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't sense\nanything suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:31.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll bet you're hiding something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:33.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Long ago, my father told me\nof demons who
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,realize their power for the first\ntime after death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For the first time after death?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:45.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The most recent demon\nwe destroyed was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:46.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:52.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then that weak, giant centipede\nis the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:55.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then we must make sure\nit's permanently sealed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Myoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:06.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:16.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:29.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's just a carcass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:32.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing scary about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:36.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, let's seal it\nwith a sutra charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:44.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, you don't have\nany luck with men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:45.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unless you leave your\ncurrent fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:50.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you won't find peace\nor happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about you, Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:58.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmmm... Let's see... Hmm...\NYou're no better with men!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:02.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd better forget about him.\NHe's too much of a womanizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:05.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your palm-reading is\nright on the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:06.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:09.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Are you done\nwith sealing the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:14.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop slacking, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!\NUnforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!\NIs this payback for earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you've shown your true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:33.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You lecher monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't think you were\nsuch a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:39.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I misjudged you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:41.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I always knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:47.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This time, the spirit of the\ncentipede has possessed Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:51.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku shows no signs\nof being possessed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:52.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,by such a strong power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:01.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, run from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't need to be told that!\NKirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:07.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away!\NHalt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:09.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:19.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I can't catch up to that\nlittle kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,this body is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:24.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with that accent, Miroku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:26.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I said he's possessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:27.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:41.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!\NAre you the real Miroku now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:45.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:52.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He has {\i1}definitely{\i0} returned\nto his old self, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel something suspicious\napproaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:14:59.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could it be the mate of\nlast night's centipede?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this the one who\npossessed us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:17.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:20.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:21.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's demon fluid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:22.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:29.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a pesky centipede!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:58.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's put a sutra charm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:08.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, everything is settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:34.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:43.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!\NYou won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:46.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could Inuyasha be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The way he's running...\nhe looks like a flea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:51.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Flea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:56.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This time, it's Inuyasha?!\NWhat's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:57.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is not Master Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:03.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:05.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:18.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't think you can escape\nfrom me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:28.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My body is all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:30.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Inuyasha! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You and I will get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:39.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I still have my own dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:42.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to fall in love...\nand I want to declare my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!\NKagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! You're back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:01.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:04.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You stupid dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:07.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:15.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:16.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:19.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please let me go, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, it's a flea!\NAn unfamiliar flea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It came out from Inuyasha's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:30.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is my one wish\nof a lifetime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:31.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:35.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga!\NIt's the end of the line for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You cannot get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:50.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh dear... This is so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:53.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm called Shoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:57.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm betrothed to Myoga.\NOur parents arranged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:58.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-No, she's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:00.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Shoga, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't call her old!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:10.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, no... When a flea reaches\nmy age,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:13.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,she wants to settle down\nand have a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From long ago, he's been\nsuch a womanizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:23.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whenever there's a pretty woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:26.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He goes to check on her\nwithout a word...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:29.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he leaves without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I came after him this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:40.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,sworn to take him back even\nif I must carry him on my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:46.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga, are you prepared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Please let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:49.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please release me, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:58.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You knew that this Old Shoga\nwas the one who bewitched us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:04.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, do you intend to\nsteal my days of youth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:06.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What days of youth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:10.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think I'd better tie\nyou to my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:10.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, now... Old Shoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. If you're going to\ntake Old Myoga's freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you should stay here\nand get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:24.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Marry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:29.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you can start a\nlife together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:31.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:33.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:36.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She may be a flea, but she's\nstill a female.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:39.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll ask the headman to\nbe the go-between.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:41.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no need for\nthe headman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:42.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:45.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga doesn't seem\npleased about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have to resign yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:50.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Become a fine flea\nhusband and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:51.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:08.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga... Now we are\nmarried at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:11.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:15.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can at least say\nyou love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:20.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:24.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:25.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:26.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:27.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Shoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:29.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:32.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He switched places with\nsome roving flea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Myoga! He ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:40.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run! Run to the depths of Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:46.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why that old geezer!\NWait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:51.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:55.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:58.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:02.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That flea! When it comes\nto running away, he's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:08.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:09.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:52.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... Can't you find\NNaraku's castle yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:54.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me!\NI can't concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.11,0:23:55.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the night of the\nnew moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:57.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is your sense of smell\nlost for this night?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:23:59.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.78,0:24:02.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! This smell... It belongs\nto Koga of the Wolf-Demon Tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.69,0:24:03.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:04.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:06.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura is making a deal\nwith Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:12.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Naraku's Barrier... Kagura's Decision"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.90,0:24:14.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, of all times!
